{"tid":2099741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"支持方EE𠝹死李梓敬條仆街，一齊叫屋企藍絲撐EE","createTime":"2020-07-08T12:56:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T14:29:57.000Z","uid":256533,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a048b9fd2742d1a49a959df7f6728a8bb3217d8","tid":2099741,"uid":256533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:56:05.000Z","msg":"<strong>【立法會選舉2020】方國珊擬6度戰立會｜貼地民生自成一派唔玩政治｜「欺師滅祖」轉贈李梓敬</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>方國珊：李梓敬恨做立會議員變得好「民建聯」</strong><br />\n/ 提到李梓敬，方國珊表示自己當年還在自由黨時，看住對方加入，但認為他現時「好恨做立會議員，脫離咗以前在自由黨時的軌跡，變得好『民建聯和工聯會』。」方國珊坦言，很難想像李梓敬自由黨出身但現時路線很左，「像何君堯一樣很異類。」方國珊更指，「他以前曾說過我欺師滅祖，我覺得這句話現在很合適他，想送這句說話給他。」<br />\n<br />\n方國珊續指，其實自由黨過去給了他不少機會，上屆立法會選舉時，田北俊更排他名單第二為他抬轎，「他當時知名度不高，要倚重田生（田北俊），我自己當時在自由黨也未試過有這樣的待遇。」方國珊指，自由黨為他付出了那麼多，他離黨代表新民黨出選做法令自由黨失望。方國珊認為，從政的人應毋忘初心，指李梓敬是真正的「政治變色龍」，稱自由黨也有不少人是這樣認為。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/128099/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%892020-%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%8B%E7%8F%8A-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8-%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%B1-%E6%9D%8E%E6%A2%93%E6%95%AC-%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F.htm?fbclid=IwAR0ToyHHCzcWBmolPUb4ssek8badPhENNwYKDuQ7CNZIIeGdpF3ZPoLyuT4#utm_source=Facebook&amp;utm_medium=page&amp;utm_campaign=page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businesstimes.com.hk%2Farticles%2F128099%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%25892020-%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259C%258B%25E7%258F%258A-%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%25BB%25A8-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%259D%25B1-%25E6%259D%258E%25E6%25A2%2593%25E6%2595%25AC-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E7%2594%259F.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ToyHHCzcWBmolPUb4ssek8badPhENNwYKDuQ7CNZIIeGdpF3ZPoLyuT4%23utm_source%3DFacebook%26utm_medium%3Dpage%26utm_campaign%3Dpage&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=fabf2e66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.businesstimes.com.hk/articles/128099/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%892020-%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%8B%E7%8F%8A-%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%BB%A8-%E6%96%B0%E6%9D%B1-%E6%9D%8E%E6%A2%93%E6%95%AC-%E6%B0%91%E7%94%9F.htm?fbclid=IwAR0ToyHHCzcWBmolPUb4ssek8badPhENNwYKDuQ7CNZIIeGdpF3ZPoLyuT4#utm_source=Facebook&amp;utm_medium=page&amp;utm_campaign=page</a>"},{"pid":"3a84d424a94221bf79d6cf7345df6cd9f48098f7","tid":2099741,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:57:26.000Z","msg":"你叫咗屋企人支持邊個<br />\n做咩唔索性叫佢哋支持本土派"},{"pid":"90fc352849cc94b9b5861a91aa8caf65d4becbbc","tid":2099741,"uid":256533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a84d424a94221bf79d6cf7345df6cd9f48098f7","tid":2099741,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:57:26.000Z","msg":"你叫咗屋企人支持邊個<br />\n做咩唔索性叫佢哋支持本土派"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T12:59:21.000Z","msg":"藍到hihi點會撐本土<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbc1281b9ab6002d27f4b22bd1e4fdc35b759ab","tid":2099741,"uid":326526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"西門梓<br />\n<br />\n無叫錯"},{"pid":"ee91b9db14ff03cc655a88dcdd9157c7f87ec8a0","tid":2099741,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"哪吒屆屆都出嚟𠝹保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4e377a13ebdd29368e489787ee2b165d130ab59","tid":2099741,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee91b9db14ff03cc655a88dcdd9157c7f87ec8a0","tid":2099741,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:13:27.000Z","msg":"哪吒屆屆都出嚟𠝹保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:20:34.000Z","msg":"調番轉講, 上屆如果棄鄧家彪過票比佢已經贏左啦, 係咪可以證明佢唔算保皇??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302974386f5cdcdc16e20d3e90f005c9c1216f99","tid":2099741,"uid":1